import React from "react"; import { useState } from "react"; import { useSelector } from "react-redux"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; import { toast } from "react-toastify"; const Checkout = () => { const [username, usernamechange] = useState(""); const [Firstname, Firstnamechange] = useState(""); const [Lastname, Lastnamechange] = useState(""); const [ zip, zipchange] = useState("") const [country, countrychange] = useState(""); const [address, addresschange] = useState(""); const navigate = useNavigate(); const IsValidate = () => { let isproceed = true; let errormessage = 'Please enter the value in '; if (username === null || username === '') { isproceed = false; errormessage += ' Username'; } if (Firstname === null || Firstname === '') { isproceed = false; errormessage += ' Fullname'; } if (Lastname === null || Lastname === '') { isproceed = false; errormessage += ' Fullname'; } if(!isproceed){ toast.warning(errormessage) }else{ if(/^[a-zA-Z0-9]+@[a-zA-Z0-9]+\.[A-Za-z]+$/.test(username)){ }else{ isproceed = false; toast.warning('Please enter the valid user name') } } return isproceed; } const handlesubmit = (e) => { e.preventDefault(); let regobj = { username, Firstname, Lastname, country, address, zip }; if (IsValidate()) { //console.log(regobj); fetch(" http://localhost:3000/checkoutDetails", { method: "POST", headers: { 'content-type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify(regobj) }).then((res) => { toast.success('Registered successfully.') navigate('/'); }).catch((err) => { toast.error('Failed :' + err.message); }); } } const state = useSelector((state)=> state.handleCart) console.log(state) var total = 0; const restList = (rest) => { total = total + rest.price*rest.qty; return(
  • {rest.foodName}({rest.qty})
    ${rest.price*rest.qty}
    • ); } return ( <>

    Your cart {state.length}

      {state.map(restList)}
    • Total (USD) ${total}

    Billing address

    Firstnamechange(e.target.value)} className="form-control">
    Valid first name is required.
    Lastnamechange(e.target.value)} className="form-control">
    Valid last name is required.
    @ usernamechange(e.target.value)} className="form-control">
    Your username is required.
    Please enter your shipping address.
    Please select a valid country.
    zipchange(e.target.value)} className="form-control">
    Zip code required.

    Payment

    Full name as displayed on card
    Name on card is required
    Credit card number is required
    Expiration date required
    -
    Security code required
    Continue to checkout
    ); }; export default Checkout;
